Recopilacin de No Idea Records de 2000. Este CD recopilatorio es un extracto del Return of the Read Menace, otro disco recopilatorio del sello Honest Don's Hardly, de 1999.

== Listado de canciones de Read Army Faction ==
Hot Water Music - Springtime
Avail - Suspicious Minds
Discount - Trouble in the Sky
The Weakerthans - The Ringing of Revolution

